metadata_description: This tool extracts Credit card numbers. NTLM(DCE-RPC. HTTP. SQL. LDAP. etc). Kerberos (AS-REQ Pre-Auth etype 23). HTTP Basic. SNMP. POP. SMTP. FTP. IMAP. etc from a pcap file or from a live interface.
